06:07.208 --> 06:09.608
Sir, thanks for returning my call.

06:09.610 --> 06:11.110
I thought I told you to stay put.

06:11.112 --> 06:12.811
Don't try selling me any horse pucky

06:12.813 --> 06:13.912
about a cartel killer.

06:13.914 --> 06:15.381
You're just trying to justify

06:15.383 --> 06:17.816
going on a tear after them geckos.

06:17.818 --> 06:19.818
I'm just reading the evidence.

06:19.820 --> 06:21.854
Well, I'm standing next to a body

06:21.856 --> 06:23.889
out in the middle of nowhere,
and he's been dead about what?

06:23.891 --> 06:25.157
Looks like about two hours.

06:25.159 --> 06:26.859
Looks like he's been bled out.

06:26.861 --> 06:28.727
Did you hear that?

06:28.729 --> 06:30.929
And he's still got his eyes.

06:30.931 --> 06:32.998
That doesn't match the
killer you're tracking.

06:33.000 --> 06:34.533
Does that mean anything to you?

06:34.535 --> 06:36.135
Sir, I brought in an expert.

06:36.137 --> 06:38.470
He says we're not just
dealing with a cartel.

06:38.472 --> 06:39.938
Like, some kind of blood cult.

06:39.940 --> 06:42.941
They worship an ancient
Mexican God of death.

06:42.943 --> 06:47.880
Ranger, my son tells me lots
of crazy things when I get home.

06:47.882 --> 06:49.948
That's 'cause he's high on weed.

06:49.950 --> 06:52.017
Don't make me listen to it at work.

06:52.019 --> 06:53.952
The geckos are crossing at Acuna.

06:53.954 --> 06:56.088
They're gonna get help from this cartel.

06:56.090 --> 06:57.956
I just need you to call it in.

06:57.958 --> 07:00.192
I'll call the border boys...
If you swear to me right now

07:00.194 --> 07:02.060
you're gonna turn around and head home.

07:02.062 --> 07:04.563
Earl told me not to rest
until these geckos were dead.

07:04.565 --> 07:06.899
My hand to God, that's the
last thing he said to me.

07:06.901 --> 07:09.501
Guess I'm answering to a higher power now.

07:09.503 --> 07:10.903
Some free advice, son...

07:10.905 --> 07:14.940
You find yourself in a hole, stop digging.

07:16.776 --> 07:19.845
That said, I see why you
can't let go of the shovel.

07:19.847 --> 07:22.981
I'll call it in.

07:22.983 --> 07:25.150
But you call me soon as you got anything.

07:25.152 --> 07:26.118
Deal?

07:27.454 --> 07:28.887
Deal.

07:47.541 --> 07:49.141
I didn't get shot so these son of bitches

07:49.143 --> 07:50.909
could ride off into the sunset.

07:50.911 --> 07:52.544
You promise me something.

07:52.546 --> 07:54.079
You kill these bastards.

07:54.081 --> 07:56.982
I swear on my daughter, I will.

08:02.890 --> 08:05.824
What can I do you for?

08:05.826 --> 08:07.259
Fill 'er up.

08:12.966 --> 08:14.566
You could have dropped us off first.

08:14.568 --> 08:16.835
I mean, like, why'd you
have to park so far away?

08:16.837 --> 08:19.037
I am the driver. I park where I please.

08:19.039 --> 08:21.139
I don't even
know why you're driving.

08:21.141 --> 08:23.575
Dad half-drunk can drive
better than you ever could.

08:23.577 --> 08:25.010
Dad!

08:25.012 --> 08:26.144
What makes you think
you can talk like that?

08:26.146 --> 08:27.546
I was just kidding.

08:27.548 --> 08:29.648
We're still a clean family.

08:29.650 --> 08:30.949
Show some respect.

08:30.951 --> 08:33.184
Dad. Stop.

08:34.120 --> 08:36.020
Dad.

08:52.572 --> 08:55.307
Kate, mind if I take the bed?

08:55.309 --> 08:58.544
No, not at all. I'm going to the pool.

09:06.220 --> 09:07.286
Katey-kakes.

09:07.288 --> 09:09.688
Open the door.

09:11.190 --> 09:13.091
Now.

09:22.201 --> 09:25.237
I'm sorry about the drink.

09:26.573 --> 09:28.640
I was just...

09:28.642 --> 09:30.909
Taking the foot off the gas, so to speak.

09:30.911 --> 09:32.945
It won't happen again.

09:32.947 --> 09:34.313
Good.

09:34.315 --> 09:36.915
Are we done?

09:36.917 --> 09:38.917
You want to tell me
what's going on with you?

09:38.919 --> 09:41.019
Nothing is going on with me.

09:41.021 --> 09:43.121
You really want to turn
the whole ship around?

09:43.123 --> 09:45.123
- Yes. I do.
- Why?

09:47.026 --> 09:49.928
I don't feel safe with you anymore.

09:49.930 --> 09:52.931
I don't feel like I can trust you.

09:52.933 --> 09:55.233
You're not acting like yourself.

09:56.970 --> 10:00.238
Katey, I'm really sorry.

10:00.240 --> 10:01.940
I really am.

10:01.942 --> 10:05.043
I think in time, you'll
look back on this trip

10:05.045 --> 10:07.045
and you'll realize how important it was...

10:07.047 --> 10:10.349
Regardless of your opinion of me.

10:11.751 --> 10:13.251
Can I change now?

10:13.253 --> 10:17.723
If there's something more
that I did to let you down,

10:17.725 --> 10:19.257
I apologize.

10:51.157 --> 10:53.191
Hey, there, old-timer. Say, listen.

10:53.193 --> 10:56.995
Um, where's a good place to get
something to eat around here?

10:56.997 --> 10:59.765
What do I look like, the
damn Chamber of Commerce?

11:00.433 --> 11:03.435
Look, I'm just trying
to find somewhere to eat.

11:03.437 --> 11:06.004
I don't care where you eat,

11:06.006 --> 11:07.406
as long as you don't eat in that room.

11:07.408 --> 11:09.307
If I smell food coming out of that room,

11:09.309 --> 11:11.309
I'm gonna throw your
ass out on that street,

11:11.311 --> 11:13.145
and don't you think I won't do it.

11:15.214 --> 11:17.215
You know what? Just forget it. It's okay.

11:17.217 --> 11:19.751
Hey, I don't need to forget
it. I've already forgot it.

11:19.753 --> 11:22.120
Don't you forget what I just told you.

11:22.122 --> 11:26.425
Okay. You have a nice day.

11:34.767 --> 11:36.234
Hey, dad.

11:36.236 --> 11:39.171
I need to get one of
the bags out of the RV.

11:45.245 --> 11:47.045
Did you order a pizza?

11:47.047 --> 11:48.346
No.

11:50.350 --> 11:52.050
Hi.

11:52.052 --> 11:54.086
You know, we're actually
in the room just below you.

11:54.088 --> 11:56.254
Do you think you could keep the
noise level down a little bit?

11:56.256 --> 11:57.889
What's that, now?

12:04.864 --> 12:07.499
The man said shut your mouth.

12:10.105 --> 12:11.170
So, what's with the Asian kid?

12:13.642 --> 12:15.141
Trick-or-treat
for UNICEF?

12:17.011 --> 12:18.678
He's my son.

12:18.680 --> 12:20.680
Really?

12:20.682 --> 12:21.848
Well, where's mom?

12:21.850 --> 12:23.116
It's just me and the boy.

12:23.118 --> 12:24.817
What about that girl?

12:24.819 --> 12:28.054
She was driving the RV, remember?

12:28.056 --> 12:29.188
Seth.

12:31.392 --> 12:33.126
You two like to play dress-up?

12:33.128 --> 12:34.994
No, we do not.

12:34.996 --> 12:36.696
Where is she?

12:36.698 --> 12:38.898
She went for a grocery
run for the motor home.

12:38.900 --> 12:40.400
She won't be back for hours.

12:40.402 --> 12:41.134
He's lying.

12:41.136 --> 12:42.201
Call her.

13:12.033 --> 13:14.033
She's not answering.

13:14.035 --> 13:15.802
She put this on before she left.

13:15.804 --> 13:17.970
She's probably at the pool.

13:19.039 --> 13:20.807
I'll go get her.

13:24.945 --> 13:26.779
Actually...

13:26.781 --> 13:28.815
You go get her, Richie.

13:28.817 --> 13:30.950
You spent enough time in hotels today.

13:35.189 --> 13:36.255
Hey.

13:36.257 --> 13:37.790
I need you to just go find her,

13:37.792 --> 13:39.192
and you bring her back here, okay?

13:39.194 --> 13:41.094
Don't talk to her. Don't touch her.

13:41.096 --> 13:42.995
Let's get on the clock.

13:42.997 --> 13:44.330
10:00 on the Timex.

13:46.734 --> 13:48.968
I've got this under control.

